study_design_info.intervention_model_description:
Study type: Interventional, with four arms:
arm: 4 mg zoledronic acid annually plus colaren ® in HIV-positive;
arm: 4 mg zoledronic acid annually plus conventional treatment in HIV-positive;
arm: 4 mg zoledronic acid annually plus colaren ® in HIV-negative;
arm: 4 mg zoledronic acid annually plus conventional treatment in HIV-negative.
